  "title": "Sales Executive/ Consultant (Construction, Technology)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>Assess client requirements within the AEC sector and propose appropriate BIM or digital construction solutions.</li><li>Deliver product demonstrations and presentations, and prepare proposals or quotations.</li><li>Generate new business opportunities while nurturing strong relationships with existing clients.</li><li>Work closely with technical teams to ensure seamless project delivery and high client satisfaction.</li><li>Monitor the sales pipeline, compile reports, and meet assigned sales goals.</li><li>Keep abreast of BIM advancements, competitor activities, and industry trends.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in Engineering, Architecture, Construction Management, or any related fields.</li><li>Minimum 2 years in sales experience in construction technology or software.</li><li>Excellent communication and presentation skills</li></ul><p>Interested applicants for the above advertised position(s), please kindly email an updated copy of your resume to: <strong>gs1@talenttradersg.com;</strong></p><p><br /></p><p>EA License No.: 13C6305</p><p>Registration No.: R23117856 CHOE KIN MUN</p><p><br /></p><p>For candidate who applied for the advertised position is deemed to have consented to us that we may collect, use or disclose your personal information for purpose in connection with the services provided by us.</p>",
